OL,3,CMcNally murder trial told how accused
OL,4,Cgrieved with family in days after
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FThe boyfriend of Natalie McNally spent
OL,8,F15-20 minutes alone with her coffin at
OL,9,Fher wake after her family "welcomed"
OL,10,Fhim into their home and treated him as
OL,11,F"a grieving partner and father to be,"
OL,12,Fa court has been told.
OL,14,FOver two days of evidence, Belfast
OL,15,FCrown Court was told how Natalie was a
OL,16,F"very strong girl who loved animals,
OL,17,Freading and music," by her family.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
