CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772718049
OL,3,CMcNally murder trial told how accused
OL,4,Cgrieved with family in days after
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, an aunt of Natalie
OL,8,Fdescribed how during the wake she told
OL,9,FMcCullagh that Bernie, Natalie's
OL,10,Fmother "didn't think he was involved"
OL,11,Fand she told him "I'm sorry for what
OL,12,Fyou have gone through".
OL,14,FA cousin of Natalie's also gave
OL,15,Fevidence.
OL,17,FHe described being in the garden of
OL,18,FNatalie's parents on the January 7,
OL,19,F2022 with the defendant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
