PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772718049
OL,3,CMcNally murder trial told how accused
OL,4,Cgrieved with family in days after
OL,5,Ckilling
OL,7,FHe told the jury how Stephen McCullagh
OL,8,Fwas distraught and was watching the
OL,9,FYouTube stream from December 18. He
OL,10,Fsaid he then fast forwarded the
OL,11,Frecording and said "this is around the
OL,12,Ftime Natalie would've been murdered. I
OL,13,Fshould've been there to protect
OL,14,FNatalie. No man would've got passed
OL,15,Fme".
OL,17,FThe cousin told Mr McCullagh he had
OL,18,F"struck gold" meeting Natalie because
OL,19,Fshe was brilliant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
